name: Emperor Julian the Apostate
description: The last pagan emperor of Rome. Constantine the Great's grandson.

name: King Ermanarich
description: King of the Ostrogoths. Expanded the Ostrogoth Empire from the Baltic to the Caspian, but then got over-ambitious when he tried to encroach upon the Huns.

name: Stilicho the Vandal
description: A Germanic general paid to fight for Rome. Fought against King Alaric

name: King Alaric
description: King of the Visgoths. Led his people to revolt against their Roman overlords
